p: Other terpenes: no sesquiterpene hydrocarbons were identified in EWs, in agreement with their insolubility in water. In EOs, very low percentages of β-caryophyllene (≤0.07%) in all samples, and slightly higher amounts of alloaromandrene in Eucalyptus pulverulenta Sims (0.44%) and Eucalyptus pulverulenta baby blue Sims (0.60%) were detected.
